<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This standard is prescribed in accordance with the provisions of Article 17 of the Act Governing Food Sanitation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[For foods which have their own sanitation standards, those standards shall be applied to the respective foods.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Products shall have their original pleasant flavor and color. No putridity, discoloration, off odor or flavor, contamination, moulds, foreign matter or parasite shall be found.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The maximum level of microorganism:

┌─────────────┬────────┬───────┐
│        ＼    Item        │MPN of Coliform │MPN of E. Coli│
│Category  ＼              │bacteria per    │per gram      │
│            ＼            │gram            │              │
├─────────────┼────────┼───────┤
│General foods served      │Not more than   │Negative      │
│without preparing         │  3             │              │
│treatments (including     │10              │              │
│washing, peeling, heating,│                │              │
│cooking, etc.)            │                │              │
├─────────────┼────────┼───────┤
│General foods to be served│                │              │
│after preparing treatments│                │              │
│(including washing,       │      －        │      －      │
│peeling, heating, cooking,│                │              │
│etc.)                     │                │              │
└─────────────┴────────┴───────┘

]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standard shall be implemented from the date of promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
